import { Container } from "./Container.style";
import { Grid } from "./Grid.style";
import { GridItem } from "./GridItem.style";
import { Input } from "./Input.style";
import {Button} from "./Button.style"

export const Register=()=>{
    return(
        <>
            <Container>
                <Grid cols="1fr" rows="1fr 1fr 1fr">
                    <Grid cols="1fr 8fr">
                        <GridItem >Email    </GridItem>
                        <GridItem ><Input/></GridItem>
                    </Grid>
                    <Grid cols="1fr 8fr">
                        <GridItem >Username</GridItem>
                        <GridItem ><Input/></GridItem>
                    </Grid>
                    <Grid cols="1fr 8fr">
                        <GridItem >Password</GridItem>
                        <GridItem ><Input/></GridItem>
                    </Grid>
                    <Grid cols="1fr 8fr">
                        <GridItem >Confirm Password</GridItem>
                        <GridItem ><Input/></GridItem>
                    </Grid>
                    <GridItem>
                        <Button/>
                    </GridItem>
                </Grid>

            </Container>
        </>
    )
}
